channel.title: RuneSpawn - Anthony
channel.description:
Hello everyone on MoparScape. Im Anthony and im 15. Apparently ive decided to come back to Runescape private servers. This project will be based on coding the most unique and best runescape spawn server/PVP. Coder's will get administrator ingame and help me code. They can get paid once i get some decent amount of money. Ill be hosting and everything, ill be also making the website.
SORRY FOR POSTING IN THE WRONG SECTION DIDNT MEAN TO!!!!
THE BASE WILL BE PROJECT-INSANITY.
Im also looking for one Forum Developer to help me with coding forums.
Available Spots:
[code]Forum Developer [1] Server Coder [2] Moderator Ingame [1 for now][/code]
If your interested to apply please post with the following format.
[code]Real Name: Age: Applying for: Experiences: Msn/Skype:[/code]
Thank you, Anthony.
